{"_path":"/guide/g010","_dir":"guide","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"如何選購醬油","description":null,"image":"/images/guide/g010-1.jpeg","sequence":10,"category":"飲食健康","author":null,"link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"生活指引"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-08-07T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"如何選購醬油"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何選購醬油"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"醬油的類別"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"醬油的類別"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.edh.tw/article/35505"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"早安健康"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/01/31: 醬油怎麼挑？專家教 5 訣竅挑選天然好醬油，但 1 隱藏殺手「超傷身」:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"醬油依製程主要可分為釀造醬油與化學醬油兩種類型。根據行政院食品安全辦公室資料，傳統釀造醬油需在自然環境下緩慢發酵，成品又香又甘醇，但製程時間久、費人工、占空間，因此價格也相對較高。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"食藥署資料也介紹 4 種不同的醬油類型，風味各有差異，可依喜好與預算自行購買喜歡的醬油。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"釀造醬油"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：以大豆等含植物性蛋白質原料，經過長時間製麴發酵而成的醬油。可聞到微微發酵香氣、風味有層次、會回甘，搖動醬油時泡沫綿密、不易散去。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"化學醬油－水解醬油"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：以大豆等植物性蛋白質原料，經過酸或酵素水解，再進行調味，未經發酵製成，屬於化學醬油。風味相對發酵醬油差，較有刺鼻味。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"化學醬油－速成醬油"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：以大豆等含植物性蛋白質原料，經過酸或酵素水解，再經發酵後製成，屬於化學醬油。風味較死鹹，搖動醬油時泡沫大，且很快就散去。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合型－調和醬油"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：混合任兩種醬油製成，一般為以胺基酸水解液為原料，添加純釀醬油而成。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"醬油選購要點"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"醬油選購要點"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果不想買到化學醬油，還有哪些分辨方式？食療養生專家王明勇透露 5 個訣竅，能直接區分釀造醬油與化學醬油，也能選到較純、添加物較少的優質醬油。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成分有「大豆酸水解物」的不要買：化學醬油以鹽酸或酵素水解製成，若成分中有「大豆酸水解液」或「酸水解胺基酸液」等類似字樣，就很可能是化學醬油。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成分愈簡單愈好：釀造醬油的主要成分為大豆、穀類、砂糖、食鹽。可觀察醬油成分標籤，越簡單代表添加物越少，醬油也越單純。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"檢查沉澱物：天然釀造的醬油有時會有自然沉澱的現象，可在瓶底發現一些豆渣的沉澱物，僅影響美觀、不影響美味。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"摸瓶身：純釀造醬油大多不添加防腐劑，且製作完成後需高溫殺菌，多以玻璃容器填裝；化學醬油則常使用塑膠瓶，有塑化劑汙染疑慮。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用鼻子、舌頭把關：純釀醬油是天然發酵而成，有淡淡的豆香味，入菜料理不死鹹且回甘香醇；而化學醬油則容易有刺鼻的鹹味，甚至感覺酸苦死鹹。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"g010-1.jpeg","src":"/images/guide/g010-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"醬油評比"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"醬油評比"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"依據 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tw.my-best.com/114463"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"mybest"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 專家監製 10 大醬油推薦排行榜 2024"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.shopkimlan.com/products/%E9%87%91%E8%98%AD%E9%BC%93%E8%88%8C%E9%86%AC%E6%B2%B9-590ml"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"金蘭 鼓舌醬油"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"g010-2.jpeg","src":"/images/guide/g010-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水餃沾醬 選擇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"g010-3.jpeg","src":"/images/guide/g010-3.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=B6wC--qfYuM"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網路流傳各式水餃沾醬試吃！ 詹姆士"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"水餃沾醬自行調配：醬油 1、醋 3、香油兩三滴，覺得太鹹就加一點水"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"如何選購醬油","depth":2,"text":"如何選購醬油","children":[{"id":"醬油的類別","depth":3,"text":"醬油的類別"},{"id":"醬油選購要點","depth":3,"text":"醬油選購要點"},{"id":"醬油評比","depth":3,"text":"醬油評比"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:guide:g010.md","_source":"content","_file":"guide/g010.md","_extension":"md"}